title: Pilot
description: Angela Chase begins a friendship with Rayanne Graff and Rickie Vasquez. At home there is tension between her and her mother.

title: Dancing in the Dark
description: Rayanne arranges for Angela and Jordan to meet under the pretense of Jordan selling Angela a fake ID. Meanwhile, Angela's parents take ballroom dancing lessons.

title: Guns and Gossip
description: A gun goes off in school, and Rickie is involved. A rumor makes the rounds at Liberty High that Angela slept with Jordan.

title: Father Figures
description: Angela gives her father the silent treatment, and Patty must deal with her own father when the printing shop is audited by the IRS.

title: The Zit
description: A list makes the rounds at school rating the sophomore girls; Rayanne and Sharon are on it, but not Angela. Patty wants Angela to join her in a mother-daughter fashion show.

title: The Substitute
description: A substitute teacher captures the hearts and minds of Angela's English class, but he may not be all he seems to be.

title: Why Jordan Can't Read
description: Patty thinks she may be pregnant, and Angela learns of Jordan's reading problem.

title: Strangers in the House
description: Sharon moves in with the Chases after her father has a heart attack.

title: Halloween
description: Angela fears that Jordan may be expelled, and she has visions of a Liberty High student who died years earlier.

title: Other People's Mothers
description: Angela wants to go to Rayanne's party, but is stuck at a party for her grandparents instead. Meanwhile, Rayanne's drinking starts to spiral out of control.

title: Life of Brian
description: Brian is caught between taking Angela or a new girl at school to a dance. Rickie has a crush on a new student at Liberty High.

title: Self-Esteem
description: Angela ignores her schoolwork to spend time making out with Jordan in the infamous boiler room, but Jordan doesn't want his friends to know that they're together.

title: Pressure
description: Angela feels pressured by Jordan to have sex.

title: On the Wagon
description: Angela and Rayanne start to grow apart, and Rayanne joins Jordan's band. Patty worries that Rayanne may have started drinking again.

title: So-Called Angels
description: Rickie finds himself homeless on Christmas, and Angela tries to help him with the aid of a mysterious homeless girl.

title: Resolutions
description: It's a new year, and everybody's making resolutions. Rickie finds himself homeless once again, and Brian finds himself tutoring Jordan.

title: Betrayal
description: Rayanne wins a role in the school play, but betrays Angela by sleeping with Jordan. Patty suspects Graham and Hallie's relationship may be more than professional.

title: Weekend
description: Angela's parents leave town for the weekend, and Rayanne accidentally handcuffs herself to their bed.

title: In Dreams Begin Responsibilities
description: Brian writes a letter to help Jordan win Angela back, Delia has a crush on Rickie, and Graham's cooking impresses the restaurant's investors.
